  speakerName: "K\xF6yl\xFC"
  dialogueText: "Hayatta kalmak istiyorsak bu \u015Fehirden ka\xE7mam\u0131z gerekiyor.
    Ancak canavarlar her yerde, \u015Fans\u0131m\u0131z \xE7ok az..."
  choice1Text: '*sessiz kal*'
  choice1NextNode: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 83d28d3e4e5e8074fa3112086f5361bf, type: 2}
  choice2Text: "Karde\u015Fim, kalbini Tanr\u0131'ya ver. Tanr\u0131 kalbinde ya\u015Fad\u0131\u011F\u0131
    s\xFCrece umut da orada olacakt\u0131r."
